4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aimed at becoming cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. Courses cover essential topics including Windows, Linux, network security, penetration testing, and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Participants receive an official completion certificate upon finishing the program. Both English and Spanish options are available for the syllabus and content. The median annual salary for cybersecurity professionals in the U.S. is approximately $103,560. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop